      <title>中国通过创纪录的香港票据发行加大对人民币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国加大了对陷入困境的人民币的支持，计划在香港市场发行创纪录数量的人民币钞票，以增加海外对人民币的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>看跌押注导致印度卢比对冲成本创 2022 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的人押注印度当局正在放松对卢比的控制，对冲印度资产外汇风险的成本升至两年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利财富管理部门的 Chui 谈亚太战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/morgan-stanley-wm-s-chui-on-apac-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利亚太区财富管理主管 Vincent Chui 讨论了他对亚洲业务扩张的展望，并表示他们的重点是 2025 年大中华区的财富领域。他在香港摩根士丹利亚洲财富峰会间隙就“彭博：亚洲交易”进行了采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/morgan-stanley-wm-s-chui-on-apac-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金在可能影响利率路径的美国数据公布前保持两天涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gold-holds-two-day-gain-before-us-data-that-may-shape-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在本周晚些时候公布的关键就业数据之前仔细考虑美联储的宽松路径前景，金价在连续两天上涨后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gold-holds-two-day-gain-before-us-data-that-may-shape-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚部长称 2025 年经济增长将超过 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/malaysia-minister-says-growth-set-to-surpass-5-in-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚第二财政部长阿米尔·哈姆扎·阿齐赞在吉隆坡接受彭博社哈斯琳达·阿敏的独家采访时表示，马来西亚的经济增长将保持去年的水平，到 2025 年将超过 5%，因为强劲的外国直接投资和本地基金的支持将保护马来西亚经济免受任何全球风险的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/malaysia-minister-says-growth-set-to-surpass-5-in-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银旗下芯片设计部门考虑收购 Ampere Computing</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/chip-designer-arm-considers-acquiring-ampere-computing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，软银集团公司及其多数股权的 Arm Holdings Plc 正在探索收购 Ampere Computing LLC 的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/chip-designer-arm-considers-acquiring-ampere-computing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称爱尔兰房屋要价涨幅创 2022 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/irish-home-asking-prices-rise-at-highest-rate-since-2022-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告显示，爱尔兰房屋要价在最后一个季度上涨至 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，交易活动接近爱尔兰凯尔特之虎增长时期的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/irish-home-asking-prices-rise-at-highest-rate-since-2022-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴亚洲货币将失去对冲成本的支撑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/emerging-asian-currencies-set-to-lose-support-from-hedging-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元投资者对冲亚洲投资的成本预计将从两年来的高位回落，这一转变可能会导致对该地区货币的支持减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/emerging-asian-currencies-set-to-lose-support-from-hedging-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在震荡后下跌，年初涨势消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在经历了一个动荡的交易日后小幅走低，因为交易员们评估自新年以来的涨势是否过快，而最大进口国中国公布的数据凸显了经济面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 23:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
